    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂停对洛杉矶无家可归者机构的资助</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/trump-los-angeles-homeless.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府将支出不当列为阻止向洛杉矶无家可归者服务管理局提供资金的原因之一。市长凯伦·巴斯警告说，“人们将会失去生命。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/trump-los-angeles-homeless.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 02:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼迪中心上诉删除特朗普名字的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/arts/music/kennedy-center-appeal-trump-name.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在将总统名字从正面去掉的最后期限前一天，这家艺术机构对联邦法官的裁决提出上诉，该裁决也暂时阻止了该机构关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/arts/music/kennedy-center-appeal-trump-name.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 01:40:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关于特朗普挑选的情报总监杰伊·克莱顿（Jay Clayton）你需要了解什么</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/what-to-know-jay-clayton.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克莱顿是曼哈顿的联邦检察官，也是美国证券交易委员会前主席，他一直监管着一个以处理重大案件而闻名的办公室。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/what-to-know-jay-clayton.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 00:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在对比尔·普尔特的强烈反对后，特朗普任命杰伊·克莱顿为国家情报总监</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/trump-jay-clayton-intelligence-chief.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统表示，他将提名曼哈顿联邦检察官、证券交易委员会前主席杰伊·克莱顿(Jay Clayton)担任永久职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/trump-jay-clayton-intelligence-chief.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 22:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界杯正式开打</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/briefing/world-cup-trump-spy-chief.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此外，特朗普还挑选了一位新的情报局长。这是周四月底的最新消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/briefing/world-cup-trump-spy-chief.html</guid>
