    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 最终确定 IPO 价格为每股 135 美元，这是全球最大规模的公开发行</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/technology/spacex-ipo-price.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的火箭公司表示，将在其大规模首次公开募股中以每股 135 美元的价格出售超过 5.55 亿股股票，该股票定于周五开始交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/technology/spacex-ipo-price.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 21:38:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邮政服务提出在不移交数据的州阻止邮寄选票的提案</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/usps-mail-voting-democratic-resistance.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党和投票权团体对拟议的规则提出质疑，称其为有害的联邦干预，可能会影响数以百万计通过邮寄投票的选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/usps-mail-voting-democratic-resistance.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 20:39:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>怀疑者质疑 SpaceX 是否值 1.77 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/technology/spacex-valuation-skeptics.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的火箭公司投入巨资，但仍在亏损。这引发了人们的疑问：该公司能否证明其大规模首次公开募股的估值合理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/technology/spacex-valuation-skeptics.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 20:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部限制其对州选举的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/trump-california-vote-elections-investigations.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该部门曾试图避免参与州选举，并敦促谨慎行事。随着特朗普总统重申其毫无根据的选举不可信的断言，该机构现在正在推进欺诈指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/trump-california-vote-elections-investigations.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 19:44:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
